> {%
    // This script catches the token from your live server and saves it!
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.access);
%}


### 2. Trigger the AI Substitution
POST https://grist-diet-app-production.up.railway.app/api/meals/1/substitute/
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ingredient_to_replace": "tempeh"
}